jobs_results.title: Flutter Developer
jobs_results.description:
This a Full Remote job, the offer is available from: European Union

Who we are
We’re an award-winning development agency at the heart of Vilnius City with clients all around the world. Being a premier development agency we only work for the best, with the best. We specialize in web & mobile development and bespoke UX/UI design. No matter how big or small our client’s organization and budgets are, we’ve got a solution for them. This means you have a chance to work with both small and medium-sized businesses. We also provide outsourcing & outstaffing services to our clients.
What we are looking for
Looking for a Flutter developer for a full-time job as a contractor in our clients team.

Day to Day
• Flutter application development
• Working together with other developers, project manager and UX/UI designer to build smooth & scalable app
• Learn best software development practises with your colleagues
• Contribute to quality by identifying spots of improvements
• Experience with REST API, HTTPS
You are someone who has...
• At least 2 years experience as a Software Developer
• At least 2 year experience with Flutter SDK and Dart language
• Rich experience in different screens layouting/supporting
• Experience in building at least 1 Android and/ or iOS application using Flutter
• Understanding and experience with state-management patterns: Provider, BLoC / MobX
• Strong experience with Git / Git Flow
• Strong communication, problem-solving skills
• Fluency in English language
• Experience (as an advantage) with Flutter for Web, Flutter for Desktop/ Flutter Platform Channels; in Android development (Android SDK)/ iOS development (Xcode, iOS SDK); with Agile methodologies (Scrum, Kanban)
Why you’ll love working with Scale3C
• Work with some of the world’s leading and most recognized brands
• Have the opportunity to work 100% remote from any country around Europe
• Office in Vilnius city center
• Cool and vibrant work environmentInterested in the position? We are looking forward to your application, to connect and talk more!

Best regards,
Talent acquisition team

jobs_results.title: mobilní vývojář iOS/Android
jobs_results.description:
Jsme SVSys, malá firma, která se v IT světě pohybuje už více jak 10 let a podle čeho nás poznáte? Podle toho, že co děláme, děláme fakt dobře a umíme to!

Protože nám do cesty přišla nová výzva, hledáme do týmu kolegu, který by se jí nebál a spolu s námi by jí zdolal.

Pro nově vznikající projekt hledáme do týmu kolegu, kterého baví mobilní aplikace a vyzná se v platformách Android/iOS.

Kdo jsme my?

SVSys je malá firma, které záleží na svých zaměstnancích. Naše firma je o lidech. A proto se navzájem podporujeme a táhneme za jeden provaz

Jaké jsou benefity?

Proč pracovat u nás?

Pokud hledáš uvolněné prostředí s výborným zázemím, kde se o lidi starají, tak pojď k nám. Děláme projekty od A-Z a proto u nás dostaneš šanci dělat i věci, ke kterým by jsi se normálně ve velkých firmách nedostal. Máš tedy možnost vyvíjet vyladěná řešení na míru a díky tomu tvoje implementace bude vidět a bude jí využívat milion lidí.

Co na oplátku nabízíme my?

Osobní přístup, uvolněné prostředí se zázemím, zajímavé platové ohodnocení, možnost práce na OSVČ, flexibilní pracovní doba či HO.

Práce pro české i mezinárodní klienty. Neumíš dobře anglicky? Nevadí máme u nás možnost firemní angličtiny.

Zaujala tě tato nabídka? Tak neváhej a pojď k nám.

jobs_results.title: Android Developer for Mobile Solutions
jobs_results.description:
We are seeking a highly skilled Android developer to join our mobile team at Ringier Axel Springer Tech.
Key Responsibilities
• Design, implement, test, and deploy applications for the Android platform.
• Test code for robustness, including edge cases and general reliability.
• Collaborate with team members within an agile process to deliver new features according to requirements, within budget and on time.
• Effectively communicate in written and spoken English.
Required Skills and Qualifications

We are looking for a candidate with:
• Experience in designing and implementing Android applications.
• Strong knowledge of Java and Kotlin programming languages.
• Familiarity with MVVM architecture pattern.
• Experience with Gradle build system and dependencies management.
• Ability to evaluate tasks and provide estimates.
• Excellent communication and teamwork skills.
Benefits

Ringier Axel Springer Tech offers a range of benefits to its employees, including:
• Sport subscription.
• Training budget.
